### Command Line Mode

```bash
# Download from any supported site
ph-shorts "VIDEO_URL"

# Specify quality
ph-shorts "URL" -q 720

# Custom output
ph-shorts "URL" -o my_video.mp4

# Use proxy
ph-shorts "URL" -p http://127.0.0.1:1080
```

